feat: scalable extension changelog and versioning system

- Add ExtensionManager class for centralized extension management
- Create individual CHANGELOG.md files for each extension
- Add 'versioning extension' commands: list, bump, changelog
- Extensions now use independent semantic versioning
- Automatic changelog updates when bumping extension versions
- Scalable architecture for managing multiple extensions

Extensions with independent changelogs:
- cleanup-repo: 1.1.0
- lifecycle-hooks: 1.0.0
- npm-publish: 1.0.0
- reentry-status: 1.2.0
- sample-extension: 1.0.1 (bumped for testing)
- secrets-check: 1.1.0

Usage:
  versioning extension list
  versioning extension bump <ext> --type patch
  versioning extension changelog <ext>
